OL,3,CFurther extension for government on
OL,4,CFinucane investigation
OL,6,FThe UK Government is to get another
OL,7,Fthree weeks to decide if it will set
OL,8,Fup a public inquiry into the murder of
OL,9,FBelfast solicitor Pat Finucane, the
OL,10,FCourt of Appeal confirmed today.
OL,12,FSenior judges imposed a new deadline
OL,13,Fof September 27 for the new Labour
OL,14,Fadministration to announce what form
OL,15,Fof legally-compliant investigation it
OL,16,Fplans to establish.
