OL,3,CFurther extension for government on
OL,4,CFinucane investigation
OL,6,FMr Finucane, 39, was shot dead by
OL,7,Floyalist paramilitary gunmen in front
OL,8,Fof his wife and three children at
OL,9,Ftheir north Belfast home in February
OL,10,F1989.
OL,12,FHis widow, Geraldine has fought ever
OL,13,Fsince for a full public inquiry to
OL,14,Funcover the scale of security force
OL,15,Fcollusion in one of the most notorious
OL,16,Fkillings of the Troubles.
