OL,3,CFurther extension for government on
OL,4,CFinucane investigation
OL,6,FIn July the court dismissed an appeal
OL,7,Fagainst a previous ruling that the
OL,8,Fprevious Conservative government's
OL,9,Fresponse to the Finucane family's
OL,10,Fcampaign was unlawful.
OL,12,FAt that stage a three-week timetable
OL,13,Fwas set for confirming a probe into
OL,14,Fthe murder which would meet standards
OL,15,Frequired under Article 2 of the
OL,16,FEuropean Convention on Human Rights.
OL,18,FWith Hilary Benn newly in post as
OL,19,FLabour's Secretary of State for
OL,20,FNorthern Ireland, his barrister sought
OL,21,Fan extension to that deadline.
