OL,3,CFurther extension for government on
OL,4,CFinucane investigation
OL,6,FPaul McLaughlin KC told the court on
OL,7,FFriday that the government will have
OL,8,Fagreed on its preferred position by
OL,9,FSeptember 27.
OL,11,FEstablishing a public inquiry remains
OL,12,Fon the table as a potential option,
OL,13,Fjudges were told.
OL,15,FAmid indications a decision could come
OL,16,Fas early as Tuesday next week, the
OL,17,FSecretary of State is ready to meet
OL,18,FMrs Finucane at that stage.
